headline: Entergy Arkansas powers Google's $4B investment in the state
summary: Today at a joint community celebration with state and local leaders, Entergy Arkansas announced it will power Google's planned $4 billion technology investment in Arkansas.

headline: Google to invest $4 billion in data center project in West Memphis. Everything we know
summary: Gov. Sarah Huckabee Sanders said Google's multibillion dollar investment in West Memphis is one of the largest ever made in Arkansas.

headline: Entergy (ETR): Evaluating Valuation as Earnings Optimism and Grid Modernization Fuel Market Interest
summary: Entergy (ETR) is in the spotlight as positive sentiment builds ahead of its next earnings report. The company’s broad capital plan and progress on grid upgrades are adding to the interest from investors this quarter. See our latest analysis for Entergy. Against this backdrop of positive sentiment and ambitious grid upgrades, Entergy’s recent shareholder returns tell an encouraging story. The company’s one-year total shareholder return stands at 0.4%, with the five-year total return climbing...
